flowchart LR
    ALERT[Incident Alert]

    ALERT --> TRIAGE[on-call: triage]
    TRIAGE --> SEV{severity?}
    SEV -->|SEV1| P0FLOW[P0: exec bridge + war room]
    SEV -->|SEV2| P1FLOW[P1: eng lead + comms]
    SEV -->|SEV3| P2FLOW[P2: async fix]

    P0FLOW & P1FLOW --> MITIGATE[mitigate / rollback]
    MITIGATE --> RESOLVE[mark resolved]
    RESOLVE --> PIR[post-incident review]
    PIR --> ACTION[action items]

    P2FLOW --> TICKET[create ticket]
    TICKET --> SPRINT[schedule in sprint]
